{"tid":2376254,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾鈺成：從選舉改由協商產生行政長官是退步而不是進步","createTime":"2021-01-22T15:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T09:15:32.000Z","uid":278587,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fda1b0da5439f1053009e997cf50bc85581ffaed","tid":2376254,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T15:42:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571912-20210122.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571912-20210122.htm&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5Cbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=7cb41b31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571912-20210122.htm&h=edd4a8fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571912-20210122.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會前主席曾鈺成表示，《中英聯合聲明》和《基本法》確實訂明行政長官可以通過協商產生，但規定特首產生辦法的《基本法》第45條，由3款組成，全國政協副主席梁振英只提及其中的第1款。<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成接受網媒訪問表示，第2款的三個要素是「實際情況」、「循序漸進」和「由提名委員會提名後普選產生的目標」。他認為，既然普選是最終目標，按一般人理解，從選舉改由協商產生行政長官，是退步而不是進步。<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成表示，第3款列明特首產生的具體辦法由附件一規定，反問如果特首不是按附件一的規定產生，如何符合《基本法》要求。他指出，完整解讀《基本法》第45條就不可能明天以協商產生特首。"},{"pid":"20c195ab27abd8e1b16948f769af44501a3ae185","tid":2376254,"uid":224533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T15:50:30.000Z","msg":"香港自從回歸邊方面進步過？<br />\n共產黨就係要退歩"},{"pid":"087104b2a5dc93f7d7daac988e4ae25a52f73579","tid":2376254,"uid":37413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T15:52:27.000Z","msg":"唔係不嬲都協商咗咩，共匪話比邊個做就邊個做㗎啦"},{"pid":"7cc6758b045471b37da94fc23d8b348bc4832a64","tid":2376254,"uid":327169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"係咪想顛覆國家政權?<br />\n聽黨話 跟黨走! <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5104bc96893f7ccb966abe23af9bdb18c70ea80","tid":2376254,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"是但啦<br />\nno body fucking care"},{"pid":"0c1876aacf4a88102f2d0db3de191050e367b018","tid":2376254,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T09:15:32.000Z","msg":"wfc?<br />\n<br />\n薯片民望高咁多, 又相對識理財都輸比淋病呢條撚屌"}]}